Class QuadraticExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • QuadraticExpression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class QuadraticExpression
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    This QuadraticExpression class creates quadratic expressions with coefficients a, b, c and can check if the expression if there are roots and can return the largest and smallest roots.

    2019-09-13
